90
00:06:41,670 --> 00:06:43,960
Ms. Ding, this is just a usual inquiry.

91
00:06:44,310 --> 00:06:45,440
Don't overthink it.

92
00:06:45,440 --> 00:06:46,840
During investigations,

93
00:06:46,920 --> 00:06:50,040
